How is baseball attendance affected by (1) weather conditions, (2) performance of the home team, (3) the visiting team,
  (4) and the time and day of the game.
  
Using the Chicago Cubs home field attendance during the regular season through 2015 and 2019, we will gather data and test
  assumptions to note any trends between the four criteria that were chosen.
  
